verse.lines:
{lang-eng}The cattle are lowing, the baby awakes,
but little Lord Jesus, no crying He makes;
I love thee, Lord Jesus, look down from the sky
and stay by my cradle till morning is nigh.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Be near me, Lord Jesus, I ask Thee to stay
close by me forever, and love me, I pray;
bless all the dear children in Thy tender care,
and fit us for heaven to live with Thee there.{/lang-eng}
